high_descs: Turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the plate on the counter.
Turn around, bring the plate to the fridge.
Chill the plate in the fridge.
Take the chilled plate from the fridge, bring it across the kitchen to the opposite corner, by the wooden rack.
Put the chilled plate on the wooden rack.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled plate on the wooden rack.

high_descs: Turn to your right face the counter
Pick up the plate beside the kettle
Turn around to your right then walk forward head to the fridge on your left
Open the fridge chill the plate and put it out after a few seconds
Turn to your left move forward then left then head to the shelf on your right
Put the plate on the second layer of the shelf
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled plate on the shelf

high_descs: Turn right and face the counter area to the right of the silver tea kettle.
Pick up the white plate to the right of the silver tea kettle and to the left of the gray bowl.
Turn around and move past the blue coffee maker and red toaster then turn left and face the refrigerator.

Open the refrigerator, place the plate on the top shelf to the right of the pot, chill the plate, then open the refrigerator, pick up the plate from the top shelf and then close the refrigerator door.
Turn left and move past the range and then turn right and face the shelves at the end of the counter.
Place the plate on the second shelf to the right of the credit card.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled plate on the shelf.
